com.bws.jdistil.core.datasource.database
Class DataObjectBinding

java.lang.Object
  com.bws.jdistil.core.datasource.database.DataObjectBinding

public class DataObjectBinding
extends java.lang.Object

Defines binding information for a data object. This includes a data object class, table name, column bindings for each data object property and possibly one or more dependent property and associate bindings.

Author:
Bryan Snipes
